:1738591,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2otauQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2otauQ.jpg&h=f8de90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqitauV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqitauV.jpg&h=d585024c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3ywSJj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3ywSJj.jpg&h=4f4d5713&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"去銀行 cut 就得喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe74e56ab02fdbce6738ddc2a2ae0b1ac46f901d","tid":1738591,"uid":322689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54864cfca4a3985af18c24168696193d46041ea9","tid":1738591,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T10:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2otauQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2otauQ.jpg&h=f8de90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqitauV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqitauV.jpg&h=d585024c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3ywSJj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3ywSJj.jpg&h=4f4d5713&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"無恥界醫生熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut，我以HSBC為例，做法係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 先登入HSBC網上理財（一定要電腦版，電話app不能）<br />\n2. 然後喺 &quot;我的銀行&quot; 欄目下揀 &quot;自動轉賬 &quot;<br />\n3. 揀 &quot;管理自動轉賬&quot;，然後就會見到你每月要轉賬嘅項目<br />\n4. 揀返 &quot;Medecins Sans F HK L&quot;，然後 &quot;刪除指示&quot; 再確認<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以成功cut捐款，但我唔知其他銀行網上理財係咪一樣，大家即管試吓！<br />\n<br />\n唔捐都唔夠，要攞返之前捐過嘅錢！方法如下：<br />\n可以打上card centre要求charge back返晒之前所有捐款<br />\nchargeback除咗攞返錢，商戶係要食好貴手續費<br />\n(chargeback 只限 credit card）"}]}